{"tid":899982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌你班廢老廢青坐巴士可唔可以有啲公德心呀","createTime":"2018-11-13T01:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T16:35:46.000Z","uid":209157,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fd874664dc0a213913943bba040bf1dd551b7729","tid":899982,"uid":209157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22iCUYW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22iCUYW.jpg&h=5c5d052c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頂你個肺你班仆街係咪當巴士櫈係公廁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔撚知到底係乜人先會賤格到將啲黃色嘅紙巾涉入啲隙 可以涉到咁入好明顯就係有心架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想講見到呢啲真係會令人心情好差 當你想坐埋去時見到即刻唔想坐 見到巴士冇哂位時其他人要迫於無奈坐埋去真係幾慘 你班廢老快啲死啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實都唔只想屌廢老 早幾日見到有班死廢青(應該初中左右) 應該係打完波冇耐 攞住m記啲汽水上巴士啦 ok嘅打完波好撚熱呀嘛 公共交通工具上事無忌憚咁飲飲食食我見唔少咩 體諒嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係你注意下個樽啲水唔好滴到張櫈濕鳩哂然後俾下一手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  都算啦 我落車時見到其中一條友留低咗杯可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪又要留俾下一手幫你執垃圾呀屌你個閪咩 一個二個當巴士係公廁咁 我都仲未講啲阿伯將睇完嘅報紙留低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到呢啲嘔心又冇公德心嘅行為真係唔撚鍾意唔撚開心 巴士呢啲咁高質嘅交通工具就係俾你啲人渣搞到污糟哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好心就咪失禮外星人啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606fd903d58036c0902ae58690e2786b71e421ec","tid":899982,"uid":208364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:16:46.000Z","msg":"我以為橙皮"},{"pid":"3adc10219ec36d40b6d4f77e400234a915aba554","tid":899982,"uid":149879,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pt2j8ui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPt2j8ui.jpg&h=4c25f0b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ef71b777e20d2a117816fe8cdb52ead4d600d5f","tid":899982,"uid":59857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:12:38.000Z","msg":"留俾下一手飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c2ac368725e965a65e34ea26436679ff5e413d","tid":899982,"uid":49258,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T04:11:10.000Z","msg":"剪指甲啪啪聲個啲先賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2814ea08710bd5fea1800b2960e7f75fcc2aee","tid":899982,"uid":54295,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T04:16:21.000Z","msg":"無得救啦<br />\n全部自私撚<br />\n咖哩牛腩飯，雪菜肉絲麵乜撚都有<br />\n<br />\n屌柒佢<br />\n仲問影響到你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c67ffe12188e02be200fbe01cac95fde048a0c","tid":899982,"uid":209157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97c2ac368725e965a65e34ea26436679ff5e413d","tid":899982,"uid":49258,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T04:11:10.000Z","msg":"剪指甲啪啪聲個啲先賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T04:29:49.000Z","msg":"啲指甲又要留俾下一手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0bd25fc750e257da7578e62d17813705f044be","tid":899982,"uid":209157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"放紙巾 插針 放報紙 剪指甲都齊哂 到底啲人可以有幾衰格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28e122d51d3d38095c9002b97db8c5d3da616b6","tid":899982,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T05:19:46.000Z","msg":"所以坐位真係唔好坐入面"},{"pid":"061a1afa1bacd12dee799733386501ccb1460e86","tid":899982,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T05:50:12.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"h